8
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:31,280
and can't treat other diseases.

9
00:00:32,390 --> 00:00:34,310
You're right.

10
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:39,030
The three Heavenly Tutors asked us

11
00:00:39,030 --> 00:00:41,200
to use the heart-eater grass unique to the Tianyi tribe

12
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:42,630
to make the poisonous fog,

13
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:45,200
pretending to be the Hole Ghost

14
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,850
to snatch babies under the age of one year

15
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:49,930
to expand our tribe.

16
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:53,600
I thought the Tianyi tribe would get better and better.

17
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:57,430
However, I found out that they were trying to control the Tianyi tribe

18
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,900
to make a profit for themselves.

19
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:00,280
Are you coming to us

20
00:01:00,670 --> 00:01:03,160
to get rid of those three witch doctors?

21
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:06,080
We are going to hold a blessing ceremony

22
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:08,110
for the babies who join our tribe.

23
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:10,310
I'd like to ask you

24
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,110
to expose those witch doctors in public.

25
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:14,240
Now that you know their evil deeds,

26
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,550
why don't you expose them?

27
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:18,080
The witch doctors have been here for more than a decade.

28
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,310
Their God's Blessing scam

29
00:01:20,550 --> 00:01:23,110
deceived a generation of the Tianyi tribe.

30
00:01:23,270 --> 00:01:26,640
In the Tianyi tribe, they are the embodiment of the gods.

31
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,390
Even if you tell everyone

32
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,320
the truth,

33
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,810
they won't believe it.

34
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,740
Are you saying

35
00:01:36,030 --> 00:01:37,600
the people of the Tianyi tribe

36
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,520
don't believe you?

37
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:41,000
Exactly.

38
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:42,800
That's true.

39
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,080
Did you forget it? They said the people you healed

40
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,910
were healed by the gods.

41
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:47,830
Yeah.

42
00:01:48,470 --> 00:01:50,030
What should we do?

43
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:53,080
Only by letting the people of the Tianyi tribe know

44
00:01:53,270 --> 00:01:55,390
