54
00:02:16,990 --> 00:02:18,200
His name is Song Yuan.

55
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,150
Do you know him?

56
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:22,760
He was the first warrior before you

57
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,430
