244
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,960
I wounded him this time.

245
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:14,230
He dares not get back at me.

246
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:17,710
But he would get back at you.

247
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,960
Maybe the next time he comes,

248
00:13:23,710 --> 00:13:25,440
he will not only snatch your baby

249
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:29,040
but also hurt you.

250
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,080
Immortal.

251
00:13:31,710 --> 00:13:32,590
What should we do?

252
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:39,870
You'd better move out of here

253
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,200
