267
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:29,230
So, this young man got sick again.

268
00:14:30,110 --> 00:14:32,750
The gods love people.

269
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:35,590
I'll make the sick ghost show up

270
00:14:36,590 --> 00:14:37,980
